        10/16/2008
    








First to Review
        


I really like there polo shirts with a Butterfly on the left side. They have just about every color. The quality is also great.I stopped in to look for shirts for my cousins who are out of the country and don't have access to a mall. It was perfect I went straight to the sales racks and they had some cute shirts for only $ 5.99. It couldn't get any better than that. I must have got like 10 total.The service was also great.




