        5/1/2010
    

Yay for Aero! I came here looking for sweats for the gym and got exactly what I wanted. There were lots of colorful clothes in there. Rainbows for the win! The sales staff acted a bit snotty, like they were above everyone because they worked at Aeropostale- ooh, look at them. But that doesn't include all of them. The clothes are fairly priced, so I'll come back for more. Go Aeropostale!




