        8/20/2013
    








3 check-ins
        









            Listed in Retail Therapy


Based on several experiences in this store, I can say that this location's staff are helpful and attentive. Of course, I'm only basing this on the weekday staff -- particularly during the morning/early afternoon. There always seems to be some sort of sale going on here, and you can also find coupons on the Aeropostale website. I wish the clearance racks were a bit more organized, but I don't think I've found a store that has successfully managed such a feat.




