        2/4/2017
            





Updated review



What's enticing about this store is that the t-shirts were buy 1 get 2 free today. It's a great sale!I got the t-shirts in maroon, white, and navy blue. Used their dressing room too. They were fortunately no other people waiting for the dressing room. Great sale! Will be back again, For the basics.




